Amanda Lucas (fighter) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amanda_Lucas_(fighter) 0 Amanda Lucas (born July 1, 1981) is an American professional mixed martial artist. She is the eldest daughter of movie director and producer George Lucas and film editor Marcia Lucas. Amanda_Lucas ( born July_1 , 1981 ) is an_American_professional_mixed_martial_artist . She is the_eldest_daughter of movie_director and producer_George_Lucas and film_editor_Marcia_Lucas .
